name: VoiceTickets
0:
”Alexa, ask Voice Tickets how much are Red Sox tickets in the month of May”
”How much are Bruins tickets this weekend”
”How much are Celtics tickets the week of April 1st”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: voice tickets
des: Ask this skill about ticket pricing for your favorite sports team and it will return the starting ticket pricing for the home games during the date range specified. After returning the ticket prices, you can have the skill email you links to the tickets so you can easily purchase them from your phone or computer.
